                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4787" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0758</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9224 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“逆行者”的春天：良品铺子疫情下的逆势增长</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The&#160;Spring&#160;of&#160;Novel&#160;Heroes: the Bestore’s&#160;Growth&#160;Against&#160;the&#160;Trend&#160;under&#160;the&#160;COVID-19&#160;Epidemic</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曹麒麟，袁慧，魏天舒，甄伟丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四川大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">良品铺子股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全渠道；4C理论；数字化赋能；良品铺子</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">omni-channel; 4C marketing theory; digitization empowerment; the Bestore</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年初，新冠疫情爆发，在我国传统零售行业受到巨大冲击之际，良品铺子却逆势上扬，高光“云上市”。本案例详细回顾良品铺子的成长历程，描述了从传统的线下深耕六年，到转战线上渠道，并利用数字化赋能全渠道建设，再到近年良品铺子依托自有渠道网络，结合热点事件、网红直播等形式开展多维度全方位体验感更强的营销活动等。案例还深入剖析了良品铺子在不同时期面临的主要问题以及应对策略，从中我们可以看到，正是多年的积累加上疫情期间的及时调整，全渠道建设帮助企业扩大市场、提升效率，其数字化赋能有效打通渠道壁垒，而4C理论的灵活运用则帮助企业构建起以顾客为中心的营销体系，成为良品铺子应对疫情危机逆势增长的实力之策。良品铺子的发展经验，对于休闲食品行业，甚至是整个传统零售行业都有指导和借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At the beginning of 2020, the COVID-19 epidemic broke out. While Chinese traditional retail industry was suffering a huge hit, the Bestore was rising against the trend and was listed online successfully. In this case, we first review the growing path of the Bestore. It had been cultivating offline for 6 years before opening up online channels. Then it used digitalization to empower omnichannel construction. In recent years, the Bestore has held popular marketing events with a good way of experiencing with the help of its own channel network. This case also deeply analyzes the main problems and solutions of the Bestore during different periods. We&#160;can&#160;see&#160;that&#160;thanks&#160;to&#160;the&#160;years&#160;of&#160;accumulation&#160;and&#160;the&#160;timely&#160;adjustment&#160;during&#160;the&#160;epidemic&#160;period,&#160;construction&#160;of&#160;the&#160;omni-channel&#160;helps&#160;the&#160;Bestore&#160;expand&#160;market&#160;and&#160;improve&#160;efficiency.&#160;Its&#160;digitalizing&#160;empowerment&#160;can&#160;effectively&#160;break&#160;through&#160;the&#160;channel&#160;barriers&#160;and&#160;the&#160;flexible&#160;use&#160;of&#160;4C&#160;theory&#160;helps&#160;companies&#160;build&#160;a&#160;marketing&#160;system&#160;centered&#160;by&#160;customers. The development experience of the Bestore has significance of guidance and reference for the snack food industry and even the entire traditional retail industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《企业战略管理》、《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全渠道建设和 4C 营销策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
